The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Its Yuvraj vs Dhoni
                                                                                                                                                                                           Its Yuvraj vs Dhoni
                      
	Mohali: Bitter rivals will join hands and compatriots will take on each other in what promises to be a thrilling encounter in the IPLs Twenty20 match between Kings XI Punjab and Chennai Super Kings here Saturday.         
	Super Kings skipper Mahendra Singh Dhoni will join his team on Saturday.         
	Swashbuckling left-hander and Mohali team captain Yuvraj Singh has already fired the first salvo, saying he and Dhoni may be great pals off the field but there is no friendship on the field.         
	Yuvraj, who will try to cash-in on the home support to put pressure on the Dhoni-led team, said: We want to win and have an upper hand in the competition. (PTI)                                                                                                                          
